287
00:38:01,619 --> 00:38:04,039
[SPEAKER_01] kad si ti shvatio da je to možda potencijalna pronost,

288
00:38:04,039 --> 00:38:07,800
[SPEAKER_01] koji se ti boriš ono, da je ogromna količina informacija

289
00:38:07,800 --> 00:38:10,860
[SPEAKER_01] koja ti kola glavom, količina ljudi s kojima pričaš,

290
00:38:10,860 --> 00:38:13,539
[SPEAKER_01] jer nemaš vremena za neki mir.

291
00:38:13,539 --> 00:38:15,500
[SPEAKER_00] Nedovoljno. Tako ću to govoriti.

292
00:38:15,500 --> 00:38:16,840
[SPEAKER_00] Nedovoljno kontempliram.

293
00:38:16,840 --> 00:38:20,880
[SPEAKER_00] Želim i moram više, jer vidim koliko mi dobro ga to donese.

294
00:38:20,880 --> 00:38:24,300
[SPEAKER_00] A želim si dobro. Kao što želim drugim ljudima.

295
00:38:24,300 --> 00:38:28,360
[SPEAKER_00] A taj nekakav instrument koji imamo kao molitvu,

296
00:38:28,360 --> 00:38:31,900
[SPEAKER_00] uhvatim sebe često, pogotovo kad sam jako umoran,

297
00:38:31,900 --> 00:38:35,440
[SPEAKER_00] da bude plitak, da bude nominalan,

298
00:38:35,440 --> 00:38:39,760
[SPEAKER_00] da on nije intiman, da nije razgovor koji je u odnosu.

299
00:38:39,760 --> 00:38:41,699
[SPEAKER_00] Da je to zadatak koji se odrađuje.

300
00:38:42,039 --> 00:38:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] I zbog toga bude na kraju žao, jer to nije fair.

301
00:38:44,000 --> 00:38:46,920
[SPEAKER_00] Jednostavno u odnosu s Bogom nije fair

302
00:38:46,920 --> 00:38:48,860
[SPEAKER_00] ako si površani plitak.

303
00:38:48,860 --> 00:38:52,360
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ne donosiš zapravo pravu vrijednost u tu priču.

304
00:38:52,360 --> 00:38:53,659
[SPEAKER_00] Ali gled, to je prostor za rast.

305
00:38:53,659 --> 00:38:57,920
[SPEAKER_00] Također, kad razmišljamo

306
00:38:57,920 --> 00:39:00,900
[SPEAKER_00] o toj kontemplaciji,

